data-triple-N3.o: "Showtime (occasionally abbreviated as "SHO") is an American premium cable and satellite television network that serves as the flagship service of the CBS Corporation subsidiary Showtime Networks, Inc. , which also owns sister services The Movie Channel and Flix. Showtime's programming primarily features theatrically released motion pictures and original television series, along with boxing matches, mixed martial arts events, occasional stand-up comedy specials and made-for-cable movies."@en
